<hr />

<h2 id="detailed-information">Detailed Information</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Tell your friends about @mishiesmunchies! Give them your email so that they can identify you as the referrer.</li>
  <li>After 2 boxes have purchased with your email as the referrer, you will be sent a promo code to your email. Referrals do not have to purchase 2 boxes in a single order. A promo code can be obtained by having two referrals each purchase 1 box.</li>
  <li>You can use the promo code for any future available order dates (announced on this website and @mishiesmunchies). Promo codes are entered in the order form to redeem a free box of cinnamon rolls.</li>
</ol>

